# Technical Design Document (TDD)

## AI-Powered Job Hunt

Version: 1.0
Status: Design Phase

---

# 1. Purpose

This document defines the technical architecture and implementation details for the AI-Powered Job Hunt platform.

The objective of this document is to provide sufficient design information to implement the system with minimal ambiguity and minimal rework.

---

