# 4. Data Flow

Step 1
Retrieve jobs from public sources.

Step 2
Normalize source-specific data into a standard format.

Step 3
Generate fingerprints and eliminate duplicates.

Step 4
Persist new jobs.

Step 5
Retrieve unscored jobs.

Step 6
Retrieve user preferences.

Step 7
Evaluate jobs using Ollama.

Step 8
Persist evaluation results.

Step 9
Generate notifications.

Step 10
Track application progress.

