# 7. Deduplication Strategy

Fingerprint:

lower(company)
+
lower(title)
+
lower(location)

Hash:

md5(
company +
title +
location
)

Process:

Generate fingerprint
↓
Check database
↓
Exists?
↓
Yes → Ignore
No → Insert

