# 13. Security Considerations

The system shall:

* Store secrets using n8n credentials
* Avoid hardcoded tokens
* Avoid hardcoded URLs
* Avoid proprietary AI dependencies
* Remain fully self-hosted

---

# 14. Assumptions and Constraints

Assumptions:

* PostgreSQL is operational
* Ollama is operational
* Telegram Bot API is configured
* Public job sources remain accessible

Constraints:

* No paid services
* No browser automation
* No scraping dependencies
* Minimal maintenance requirements
* Self-hosted architecture only

